# All Bittensor subnet knowledge is in @knowledge/
# Start with @knowledge/INDEX.yaml for task routing

# PwnTensor = Game AI Marketplace on Bittensor
# - Game studios bring games. Each game = one Bittensor incentive mechanism.
# - Miners compete to build the best AI agents for each game.
# - Validators run headless sims, score miners per mechanism, serve frontend.
# - protocol.py: GameStateSynapse — universal across all games (game_id routes logic)
# - reward.py: per-game scoring functions + rank normalization
# - game_registry.py: active games and their mechanism mappings
# - frontend/index.html: PacTensor (demo game, mechanism 0)

# Quick reference:
# - ALWAYS load subnet.invariants.yaml first (non-negotiable rules)
# - pwntensor.architecture.yaml for the multi-game/multi-mechanism design
# - game_adapter.yaml for the game registration contract
# - pactensor.*.yaml for PacTensor-specific details

